# Stranger Talk Project - Cursor Rules

## Core Principles
- Never delete code without explicit confirmation
- Always analyze before suggesting fixes
- Test for regressions after each fix

## Debugging Protocol
1. Check browser console and network logs first
2. Verify WebSocket connection state
3. Check permission handling (microphone, camera)
4. Test each feature independently

## Bug Priority
- Critical: Connection failures, call drops, message loss
- High: Permission errors, audio/video sync
- Medium: UI glitches, notification issues

## Output Requirements
- Explain bug cause before providing code
- Show before/after code snippets
- Include error handling
